{"tid":1162372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【好勵志】體重曾達661磅全亞洲最重 印度婦為保命成功減去462磅","createTime":"2019-05-19T23:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T05:06:20.000Z","uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"522c25e91233ea58e3043db88845bd9903f83e69","tid":1162372,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T23:18:27.000Z","msg":"全亞州最重、來自印度的婦人為了保命，用4年時間接受兩次手術，成功由661磅大減462磅，預備申請將減磅幅度列入當地的《Limca紀錄大全》。負責治療她的醫生提醒癡肥是「疾病之母」，可與癌症和愛滋病相比，不能輕視。<br />\n42歲的賈亞尼（Amita Rajani）出生時是重6磅9安士的正常嬰兒，但6歲起體重突然急升，到16歲已重277磅，無論印度或英國專家都無法找到原因。10年後她的體重更飆升至661磅，令她無法踏出家門，更成為全亞州最重女子。<br />\n接受手術前8年，賈亞尼只能躺在床上，患上超級病態肥胖症、高膽固醇、腎功能衰竭、2型糖尿病和有呼吸問題。有人介紹她找沙赫醫生（Dr. Shah）幫助，沙赫指︰「癡肥是僅次於癌症或愛滋病病毒，癡肥是所有疾病之母，女性比男性更常見。」<br />\n沙赫為賈亞尼安排兩個階段的治療，2015年賈亞尼接受首階段縮胃手術，她立刻感到有改善，體重減輕了，可以自行走路；在2017年，她接受第二階段的胃繞道手術。賈亞尼如今已沒有糖尿病或高血壓，腎臟功能亦恢復，不過她要繼續跟從健康餐單飲食。<br />\n賈亞尼如今重約200磅，她表示︰「以前我只能賴在床上，但我現在可以自力救濟了，去除贅肉後我能隨心活動，我可以穿上喜歡的衣服，過一個自己想要的人生。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190519/large/1558232883_a75b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190519%2Flarge%2F1558232883_a75b.jpg&h=7eb65023&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190519/large/1558232883_76bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190519%2Flarge%2F1558232883_76bf.jpg&h=93060e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190520/59616979\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190520%2F59616979&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1xVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=b0babcc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190520%2F59616979&h=8a703f30\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190520/59616979</a>"},{"pid":"ac6f5f3fe57171a78f8989b47f9709ad9c8a2a8b","tid":1162372,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T23:21:45.000Z","msg":"6百幾磅先係亞洲最重，咁世界最重咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71302b63d62e67191f46d228d0ef52e7e27f493d","tid":1162372,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac6f5f3fe57171a78f8989b47f9709ad9c8a2a8b","tid":1162372,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T23:21:45.000Z","msg":"6百幾磅先係亞洲最重，咁世界最重咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:27:00.000Z","msg":"我都想知世界最重係幾多"},{"pid":"1b2f8e1a0b77d1b3f5b5e67f69b8a51045822132","tid":1162372,"uid":243635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:08:53.000Z","msg":"賤肉橫生"},{"pid":"51f1813b3aad21f5ab954a19733eb81dbabbea31","tid":1162372,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71302b63d62e67191f46d228d0ef52e7e27f493d","tid":1162372,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac6f5f3fe57171a78f8989b47f9709ad9c8a2a8b","tid":1162372,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T23:21:45.000Z","msg":"6百幾磅先係亞洲最重，咁世界最重咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:27:00.000Z","msg":"我都想知世界最重係幾多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"我知美國嗰面有啲重到要去劏車場用佢地啲磅嚟磅重"},{"pid":"c1fcf70addb3bd7f6250edee5c1df6a593c8387d","tid":1162372,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51f1813b3aad21f5ab954a19733eb81dbabbea31","tid":1162372,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71302b63d62e67191f46d228d0ef52e7e27f493d","tid":1162372,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac6f5f3fe57171a78f8989b47f9709ad9c8a2a8b","tid":1162372,"uid":47029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1